WARNING:  For the purposes of demonstration, a local copy of systir.rb is
included with this example in the lib directory.  This is a hint towards how
to layout your system test directory.  Please be sure you get the latest
systir.rb from the src directory in this repository.

This is an example of how to use Systir and Watir
and Watir::Simple.

The example website runs from a single ruby script.

To see the tests run:

> ruby run.rb

This assumes you have installed WATIR using the normal method as described in it's package.


